  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ たなか・しょうぞう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n衆議院議員、栃木県会議長、社会運動家"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"04t.html\">一覧　（タ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E7%2594%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%2520%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%2580%25A0\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　栃木県の名主の長男に生まれる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　17歳で名主となり、主家の苛政に反抗、投獄される。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　上京、のち岩手県の役人となる。この間、西欧思想に触れる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「栃木新聞」を創刊。栃木県議会議員となり、のち議長に就任。国会開設を主張。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　立憲改進党に入党、第１回総選挙で衆議院議員に当選。藩閥政府を批判。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　国会で足尾銅山鉱毒事件を取り上げ、以後一貫して追及。新聞社などに働きかける。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　この問題で議員辞職、<a href=\"../1901/12jikis.html\">天皇に直訴</a>を行う。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　内閣の鉱毒調査委員会が治水計画を立てるや、水没の危機にさらされた谷中村に転居。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　栃木県の谷中残留16戸強制破壊に対して、最後まで抵抗。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
